EASTERN MEDITERRANEAN SEA.
EGYPT.
1. SEISMIC SURVEY IN PROGRESS UNTIL 11 OCT
   BY M/V OTS YEOMAN AND M/V ECOLFIUMICINOA
   TOWING 1200 METER LONG CABLE
   IN AREA BOUND BY
   31-39.15N 033-31.08E, 31-39.11N 033-44.02E,
   31-28.14N 033-43.13E, 31-29.02N 033-31.03E.
